{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_122","type":"agent_message","text":"I’m wiring the session service next. The key behavior choice is deliberate: beat generation creates revisioned candidates and leaves the stage `in_progress` until a revision is accepted, while beat refinement behaves like pitch/character refinement and creates a new selected revision immediately."}}
