{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_314","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented end to end on the current branch, with two reviewable checkpoints: `790de93` for the backend generator/persistence work and `51300fc` for the workspace UI.\n\nThe backend now has a structured Save-the-Cat beat-sheet artifact and generation flow: a canonical 15-beat model, bedtime-specific fields, Gemini-backed generation with a tested fallback path, revision persistence on the session snapshot, and session routes for generate, refine, and accept. The frontend now has a dedicated Beats stage in the workspace with generation and refinement controls, saved revision cards, a full beat-by-beat outline preview, and chat/UI action wiring so beat-sheet actions round-trip through the existing session model.\n\nVerification was broad:\n- Backend: `pytest backend/tests/test_beat_sheet_generation_service.py backend/tests/test_session_beat_sheet_service.py backend/tests/test_session_api.py -q` → `38 passed`\n- Frontend targeted: `cd frontend && npm test -- --run src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.test.tsx` → `28 passed`\n- Frontend full suite: `cd frontend && npm test` → `75 passed`\n- Lint: `cd frontend && npm run lint` → passed\n- Build: `cd frontend && npm run build` → passed\n- Browser QA: desktop and mobile checks passed against the live Docker Compose app, with screenshots at [.artifacts/webapp-qa/beat-stage.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/beat-stage.png) and [.artifacts/webapp-qa/beat-stage-mobile.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/beat-stage-mobile.png)\n\nOne caveat: `cd frontend && npm run format:check` still fails because of three unrelated pre-existing files not touched by this task. I formatted only the files changed for prompt 48. During live QA I also had to fix a local ignored `secrets.yaml` shape mismatch so the backend could boot under Docker Compose; that was not committed.\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written as the final step at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/48_save_the_cat_beat_sheet_generation/summary.md)."}}
